# This repo is the whole SN6 Resources handoff: pain points, standards, the
# composites app, datasheets, printables, and the tooling that builds them.
#
# The git root is SN6 Resources/ because the scripts in tools/ resolve their
# paths as  <tools>/../03 Work Orders/... , so they only run correctly from here.
# Note that firebase deploy still runs from inside "03 Work Orders/".
#
# Track everything except build artifacts and OS junk:

.DS_Store
.venv/
node_modules/
.firebase/
__pycache__/
*.pyc
